### H2 file-mode databases created by tests / local runs ###
**/data/

# Multi-cell deploy: real secrets per cell. The committed deploy/cells/cell.<iso>.env
# holds non-secret defaults; the operator drops actual passwords / JWT secrets
# / API keys in deploy/cells/cell.<iso>.local.env on the host, never in git.
# See deploy/README.md for the layered-config workflow.
deploy/cells/*.local.env
